The user wants a Tampermonkey userscript that:
1. Disables autoplay and loop on all video elements
2. Pauses videos that are already playing
3. Handles dynamically loaded videos using MutationObserver
4. Sets preload to metadata or none
5. Should work on page load

I need to create a complete userscript with:
- Proper Tampermonkey metadata block
- Function to process video elements
- Initial execution on page load
- MutationObserver for dynamic content
- Good comments

Let me structure this properly:

```javascript
// ==UserScript==
// @name         Disable Video Autoplay and Loop
// @namespace    http://tampermonkey.net/
// @version      1.0
// @description  Automatically disable autoplay and looping for all video elements
// @author       You
// @match        *://*/*
// @grant        none
// @run-at       document-start
// ==/UserScript==
```

The script should:
1. Define a function to process videos
2. Process existing videos on load
3. Set up MutationObserver for new videos
4. Handle both initial and dynamic content

